          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">mefloquine</ENAMEX> should not <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">drink alcohol</ENAMEX>, especially within <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">24</TIMEX>
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">h</ENAMEX> of their <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">weekly</TIMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">mefloquine</ENAMEX> dose.
          While taking mefloquine, travellers should be advised
