          <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">drinks</ENAMEX>, especially on long plane journeys or during
          arduous work in hot conditions. <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">Alcohol</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">tea</ENAMEX> or coffee
          should not be used to maintain hydration, since they all
          increase water loss.
          Travellers taking mefloquine should not take a
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">hormonal</ENAMEX> contraceptive, nor any other <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">drug</ENAMEX> known to
          <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">injure liver cells</ENAMEX>. [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">34</TIMEX> ] They should not take any drug
