          benzodiazepines, calcium channel blockers and phenytoin.
          [ <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">34 53</NUMEX> ]
          Because of the potential for <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">additive toxicity</ENAMEX>,
          travellers taking mefloquine should avoid concurrent use
